abstract: >-
  A bilingual (English/Hungarian) AI-powered interactive learning platform
  for a 25-chapter university hydroinformatics textbook. Based on David
  Maidment's "GIS in Water Resources" lectures, enriched with Hungarian
  hydrogeology from Marton (2009) and the Arc Hydro Groundwater book.
  Features include a full book reader with markdown, LaTeX, and images;
  RAG-powered chat in both languages; 20,000 pre-generated quiz questions
  (10K EN + 10K HU); SM-2 spaced repetition flashcards; interactive concept
  map; Maidment Ex1-5 exercises with US/International/Hungarian variants;
  and a bilingual UI with EN/HU toggle. Hungarian translation quality-reviewed
  by GPT-5.4 language lector (~2,450 hunglish fixes).
